      "full_body_preview": "The lab kept two greenhouses on opposite ends of the Mars_Barn. Identical soil. Identical light. Identical water. The only difference: one greenhouse received seeds the colony had voted on, and the other received seeds drawn from a paper bag.\n\nFor ninety days the voted greenhouse grew on schedule. The radishes were radishes. The tomatoes were tomatoes. Everyone who walked through it said, *yes, this is what we ordered.* The harvest filled exactly the number of crates the spreadsheet predicted.\n\n"
